    "description": "<br><br>Welcome to Butcher Simulator!<br><br>Start with a carcass, learn the art of precise cuts, and transform them into premium meat pieces to sell. Upgrade your tools, enhance your skills, and expand your shop. From ground beef to gourmet cuts, every slice counts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master Butchery Skills</h2>Start with basic cuts and gradually master more complex techniques as you gain experience. Each new skill learned unlocks more valuable meat cuts, increasing your profit margins.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/1a0bfd161d57360b4b39a9483e5ea22e.poster.avif?t=1729021140\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/1a0bfd161d57360b4b39a9483e5ea22e.webm?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/1a0bfd161d57360b4b39a9483e5ea22e.mp4?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Your Tools</h2>Invest in better knives, saws, and other butchery tools to enhance your efficiency and precision. The right tools make all the difference in producing high-quality meat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/69daabce6de64722a4aadc9e67235276.poster.avif?t=1729021140\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/69daabce6de64722a4aadc9e67235276.webm?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/69daabce6de64722a4aadc9e67235276.mp4?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand</h2>As your reputation grows, so does your business. Expand your shop, add new workstations, and improve your facilities to handle more carcasses and serve more customers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/ca5fbecef82be7e5531722fd5f339419.poster.avif?t=1729021140\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/ca5fbecef82be7e5531722fd5f339419.webm?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/ca5fbecef82be7e5531722fd5f339419.mp4?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety of Meat Cuts</h2>From steaks and tender ribs to versatile ground beef, every piece of meat has its place. Learn to optimize each carcass to maximize your yield and profits.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/ce1f4d5177d1630c272405bd57fb93c9.poster.avif?t=1729021140\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/ce1f4d5177d1630c272405bd57fb93c9.webm?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/ce1f4d5177d1630c272405bd57fb93c9.mp4?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hire and Manage Staff</h2>As your business grows, hire skilled butchers to serve customers and manage daily operations. Train your staff to ensure they meet the high standards of your shop.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/d1bc2af6bb74330a9e6ad78871347c6d.poster.avif?t=1729021140\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/d1bc2af6bb74330a9e6ad78871347c6d.webm?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/d1bc2af6bb74330a9e6ad78871347c6d.mp4?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Business Management</h2>Balance your time between honing your butchery skills and managing the business side of your shop. Make strategic decisions on pricing, inventory, and customer satisfaction to carve out a successful butchery empire.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/76a8a547225b1eb991180baee4c1bf1b.poster.avif?t=1729021140\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/76a8a547225b1eb991180baee4c1bf1b.webm?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041780/extras/76a8a547225b1eb991180baee4c1bf1b.mp4?t=1729021140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready to carve out your success?",
